      "reply_to_account_id": null,
      "quoted_tweet_id": null,
      "retweeted_tweet_id": null,
      "text": "We’re cracking down hard on SNAP fraud to protect hardworking taxpayers and ensure benefits go to those who truly need them.\n\n@USDA and @OIGUSDA efforts have led to nearly 1,000 arrests tied to SNAP fraud investigations. We’re not stopping there.\n\nNow, we’re zeroing in on retailer fraud and the bad actors trafficking benefits or abusing the system. We’ve already disqualified thousands of non-compliant stores and blocked hundreds of millions in fraudulent transactions.\n\nTogether with @VP and the White House Task Force to Eliminate Fraud, we are ending abuse of public benefits. Every dollar saved strengthens the program and preserves it for American families most in need.",
      "text_resolved": "We’re cracking down hard on SNAP fraud to protect hardworking taxpayers and ensure benefits go to those who truly need them.\n\n@USDA and @OIGUSDA efforts have led to nearly 1,000 arrests tied to SNAP fraud investigations. We’re not stopping there.\n\nNow, we’re zeroing in on retailer fraud and the bad actors trafficking benefits or abusing the system. We’ve already disqualified thousands of non-compliant stores and blocked hundreds of millions in fraudulent transactions.\n\nTogether with @VP and the White House Task Force to Eliminate Fraud, we are ending abuse of public benefits. Every dollar saved strengthens the program and preserves it for American families most in need.",
